OL,3,CEngland fan in court after returning
OL,4,Cfrom Euro 2024 in Germany
OL,6,FAn England football fan from Bolton
OL,7,Fhas been bailed by a court following
OL,8,Ftrouble at the Euro tournament in
OL,9,FGermany.
OL,11,FGordon Thomas, 39, made the brief
OL,12,Fappearance at Manchester Magistrates'
OL,13,FCourt for a hearing where police
OL,14,Fapplied for a Football Banning Order,
OL,15,Fstopping him from attending matches
OL,16,Ffor the next three years.
OL,18,FDistrict Judge Joanne Hirst asked the
OL,19,Fdefendant: "Do you oppose this
OL,20,Fapplication?"
