OL,4,Cfrom Euro 2024 in Germany
OL,6,FThomas replied: "Well, I have not seen
OL,7,Fwhat they said I have done."
OL,9,FTrouble broke out between football
OL,10,Ffans following England's one-nil
OL,11,Fvictory over Serbia in Gelsenkirchen
OL,12,Fon Sunday evening.
OL,14,FVideos on social media showed
OL,15,Fsupporters clashing on a side street,
OL,16,Fwith tables, chairs and bottles being
OL,17,Fthrown before riot police arrived on
OL,18,Fthe scene ` seven Serbia fans were
OL,19,Falso arrested after violent clashes.
