OL,6,FThomas, from Little Lever, Bolton,
OL,7,Fsaid he was stopped at Manchester
OL,8,FAirport on Monday night after flying
OL,9,Fback to the UK from Amsterdam.
OL,11,FHe told the court after landing back
OL,12,Fin the UK at 8pm on Monday, his
OL,13,Fpassport was seized and he was handed
OL,14,Fpapers informing him the police were
OL,15,Fapplying for a banning order and the
OL,16,Fcase would be heard at the court on
OL,17,FTuesday.
