OL,3,CEngland fan in court after returning
OL,4,Cfrom Euro 2024 in Germany
OL,6,FDistrict Judge Joanne Hirst told
OL,7,FThomas: "This is not a criminal
OL,8,Fmatter, it is a civil complaint by the
OL,9,Fpolice to impose a Football Banning
OL,10,FOrder, it is said they can provide
OL,11,Fevidence you caused or contributed to
OL,12,Fdisorder in the UK or elsewhere.
OL,14,F"Obviously, you need to know exactly
OL,15,Fwhat you are being accused of, I
OL,16,Funderstand there's some CCTV, some
OL,17,Fstatements, will be sent to you.
OL,26,@oD@IOUvD@AOU
