OL,4,Cfrom Euro 2024 in Germany
OL,6,F"Football Banning Orders are quite
OL,7,FDraconian, it would be a minimum of
OL,8,Fthree years and stop you going to a
OL,9,Ffootball match for three years.
OL,11,F"It will be so that further violence
OL,12,Fwill not be caused. You will want to
OL,13,Fsee a solicitor."
OL,15,FLaura Peers, prosecuting, said the
OL,16,Fapplication for the order was signed
OL,17,Fby the Director of Public Prosecutions
OL,18,Fand the law meant the defendant had to
OL,19,Fbe brought before a court within 24
OL,20,Fhours of the order being served.
