OL,3,CEngland fan in court after returning
OL,4,Cfrom Euro 2024 in Germany
OL,6,FDistrict Judge Hirst told Thomas she
OL,7,Fwould adjourn the hearing until a
OL,8,Flater date after he has seen a
OL,9,Fsolicitor.
OL,11,FThomas was bailed on condition he does
OL,12,Fnot leave England or Wales before his
OL,13,Fnext court appearance on August 23.
OL,15,FHe told the judge: "Can I just ask, I
OL,16,Fhave a family holiday in August.
OL,17,FWhat's the reason for withholding my
OL,18,Fpassport until after the Euros have
OL,19,Ffinished and England don't play next
OL,20,Funtil September?"
