OL,4,Cfrom Euro 2024 in Germany
OL,6,FJudge Hirst replied: "You will not be
OL,7,Fhaving your passport back or leaving
OL,8,FEngland and Wales.
OL,10,F"But see a solicitor. It doesn't mean
OL,11,Fthat condition cannot be varied. You
OL,12,Fneed independent legal advice."
OL,14,FEarlier, Mick Johnson, head of the UK
OL,15,FFootball Policing Unit, said: "This
OL,16,Faction shows the breadth of the Euro
OL,17,F2024 football policing operation and
OL,18,Fdemonstrates there are consequences
OL,19,Ffor supporters who are intent on
OL,20,Fcausing disorder.
