OL,6,F"Any UK football supporter causing
OL,7,Fdisorder in Germany which would be
OL,8,Fdeemed an offence in this country
OL,9,Fcould face police action upon their
OL,10,Freturn.
OL,12,F"We are working closely with our
OL,13,Fpolicing colleagues in Germany and
OL,14,Fhave a team of UK officers deployed
OL,15,Foverseas supporting their operation.
